==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: rú rén yĭn shuĭ, lĕng nuăn zì zhī
===Etymology===
Literally: If a person drinks the water, he will know for himself whether it is warm or cold.
===Proverb===
'''[[如]][[人]][[飲]][[水]]，[[冷]][[暖]][[自]][[知]]'''
# One must personally experience something in order to know what it's like.
===Alternate forms===
[[如人饮水，冷暖自知]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
